Class EndgameScreenController

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.am16.client.view.gui.controllers.screens.EndgameScreenController
public class EndgameScreenController extends Object
Controller for the end game screen. The end game screen displays the amount of points for each player as well as the name of the winner(s) of the game.
